    <item>
      <title>中国2024年政策目标对中美关系意味着什么</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/what-china-s-2024-policy-goals-mean-for-ties-with-the-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国的大型年度政策报告显示，今年中国可能必须与美国友好相处，以应对经济逆风，但加大科技投资和军费开支的雄心表明紧张局势不会消失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/what-china-s-2024-policy-goals-mean-for-ties-with-the-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 10:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国推出养老金计划，基金目标为 2000 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/germany-unveils-pension-package-with-200-billion-fund-goal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国执政联盟公布了确保国家长期养老金融资的计划，其中包括设立一个股票投资基金，目标是到 2036 年价值达到 2000 亿欧元（2170 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/germany-unveils-pension-package-with-200-billion-fund-goal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 10:29:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将敲定信用卡滞纳金上限为 8 美元的规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/biden-to-finalize-rule-to-cap-credit-card-late-fees-at-8</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登总统的政府宣布了一项削减信用卡滞纳金的最终规则，这是一系列措施之一，旨在降低家庭的日常成本，这些成本在他寻求连任时影响了他的支持率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/biden-to-finalize-rule-to-cap-credit-card-late-fees-at-8</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 10:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>转向大选：超级星期二看什么</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/pivot-to-the-general-election-what-to-watch-on-super-tuesday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年的超级星期二初选将把唐纳德·特朗普推向共和党提名的风口浪尖，并展开美国近代历史上最长的大选之战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/pivot-to-the-general-election-what-to-watch-on-super-tuesday</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的一致裁决掩盖了最高法院的意识形态分歧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/unanimous-trump-ruling-belies-supreme-court-s-ideological-divide</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从表面上看，美国最高法院一致裁定唐纳德·特朗普可以参加今年的总统选举。但下方不远处，法庭上却充满了不和谐的声音。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/unanimous-trump-ruling-belies-supreme-court-s-ideological-divide</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平的名字和口号在政府重要报告中占据主导地位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/xi-s-name-favored-slogan-dominate-key-government-report</link>
      <description><![CDATA[习近平的名字今年在政府年度工作报告中出现16次，是他十多年前上任以来最多的一次，凸显了中国领导人的至高无上的地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/xi-s-name-favored-slogan-dominate-key-government-report</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 09:40:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列将出售战后第一批公开美元债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/israel-to-sell-first-public-international-bond-since-war-began</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列将于十月份与哈马斯爆发战争以来在公开市场上出售第一笔国际债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/israel-to-sell-first-public-international-bond-since-war-began</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 09:06:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾和中国在船舶再次相撞后提出贸易抗议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/philippines-says-ship-collided-with-china-coast-guard-vessel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，菲律宾和中国的船只在南海再次相撞，双方相互抱怨，进一步加剧了两国在争议海域的紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/philippines-says-ship-collided-with-china-coast-guard-vessel</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 02:31:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国将动员全国力量对抗美国科技霸主</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/china-vows-to-mobilize-nation-as-it-fights-us-for-tech-supremacy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国承诺利用全国资源加速本土科学突破，并重申在人工智能、芯片制造等领域实现自力更生，从美国手中夺取技术霸主地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/china-vows-to-mobilize-nation-as-it-fights-us-for-tech-supremacy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 01:41:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国盟友要求柏林在俄罗斯泄密后修复安全问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/german-allies-tell-berlin-to-tighten-security-after-russian-leak</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在俄罗斯披露有关向乌克兰提供军事援助的敏感讨论后，德国的一些盟友敦促柏林加强机密信息的安全。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/german-allies-tell-berlin-to-tighten-security-after-russian-leak</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 19:49:23 GMT</pubDate>
